# Screenshots

This directory is for application screenshots used in documentation.

Place screenshots here following this naming convention:

- `dashboard-dark.png` — Dashboard (dark mode)
- `dashboard-light.png` — Dashboard (light mode)
- `chat-dm.png` — Chat in DM mode
- `chat-group.png` — Chat in Group mode
- `settings-providers.png` — Settings: Providers section
- `sidepanel-open.png` — Side panel expanded
- `mobile-chat.png` — Mobile chat view

Screenshots should be:
- PNG format
- 1280×720 or 1920×1080 (desktop)
- 375×812 (mobile)
- Named descriptively